Map the Sales Process to Acquiring a Customer

How much it will cost to bring a new customer to your product?

Common Pitfalls;
> Cost behind sales + marketing required to reach prospects
> Long, expensive sales cycles
> Costs associated with customers who do NOT buy
> Cycles within customers ( Corporate shakeups, business failure) etc


